Class Moving

  • java.lang.Object
    • Moving
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    State
    public class Moving
extends java.lang.Object
implements State
    This class resembles individual's moving state. In this state individual is moving and changing location in simulation map. Since location change individual can collide with other individuals and starts conversation and change state to in conversation. Individual also can be infected, and access to hospital is granted, so individual can go hospital and stop dying. Individual also can't reach to hospital in time, so individual can die. Since individual is moving state, moveInPopulation() call doesn't effect individual.
